没有很多时间了，我们学校14号开学。而且我也不太自律。我最近在学音标。因为想开学过后就好好背单词。我有时候用平板学习 莫名其妙就会跳到其他网站了，所以我打算问完这个问题之后我就把这个软件删了，我觉得普通高中我是上得了的，但是我想重点高中，有点想的美了"},"attached_info":"Cj8IvoHmh4WKuNNrEAMaCDY3MjEwNzI5ILmzuocGMAI40QRAL3IJNDcyMTkwMzM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"48_1626822419.8263574","card_id":"Q_24190512","target":{"id":24190512,"title":"怎样学好高中数学？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/24190512","type":"question","created":1403070861,"answer_count":228,"follower_count":6738,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1291,4570,5830,31793,41299],"comment_count":8,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj0IvoHmh4WKuNNrEAMaBzE4NTgxMzIgjdOEnQUwCDjSNEAwcggyNDE5MDUxMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-11b8dc170276ab5af2ae302e0ab29788_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1626822419.8266494","card_id":"Q_457001778","target":{"id":457001778,"title":"为什么战双这么良心，流水却越来越低，甚至现在只有开服时的十分之一？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/457001778","type":"question","created":1619596209,"answer_count":156,"follower_count":247,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[401175],"comment_count":18,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IvoHmh4WKuNNrEAMaCDYzODM2MDA2ILGnpIQGMBI49wFAMXIJNDU3MDAxNzc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b3423cbfe4be6a691de729017f8bdf8b_720w.png"}]}],"description":{"time":"2021-07-21 07:07:00"}}